{"tid":864492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵大故障】港鐵：黃昏或再有信號不穩　籲乘客預留額外乘車時間 (16:53)","createTime":"2018-10-16T08:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T09:05:23.000Z","uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24ffe9749bfc4967f299199abda11f0a933beec7","tid":864492,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"港鐵荃灣線、觀塘線、港島線及將軍澳線今早接連有信號故障，致全港交通大混亂，到近中午才全線服務恢復正常。港鐵車務總監劉天成今午5時前見記者，表示黃昏繁忙時段信號仍可能不穩，候車時間或車程可能延長，呼籲乘客體諒及預留額外乘車時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab651e580843b68a9acec30431282eee1c6144e1","tid":864492,"uid":166506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  故障都有得預告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f2a0f018530adadffaf0d9d73bccee7481afa0","tid":864492,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"唔通我可以攞住呢句同我老細講，早啲收工喇 ？<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個頭盔有咩用呢"}]}